DataSource.RecordSource:
Declare @FromDate datetime, @ToDate datetime, @Year int, @Month int
Set @FromDate = '2006-07-01' Set @ToDate = '2006-07-31 23:59:59'
SET @Year = 2006 SET @Month = 7
SELECT DISTINCT locCache.LocationID, ITM_Product.ProductID, ITM_Product.Code as PartNo, ITM_Product.Description as PartName, ITM_Product.Revision as PartModel, ITM_Category.Code as CategoryCode, MST_UnitOfMeasure.Code AS StockUM,
(SUM(locCache.OHQuantity) - IsNull( (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(trans.Quantity), 0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory trans INNER JOIN MST_TranType ON trans.TranTypeID = MST_TranType.TranTypeID WHERE ProductID = locCache.ProductID AND LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND PostDate >= @FromDate AND (MST_TranType.Type = 1 OR MST_TranType.Type = 2) ) , 0) + IsNull( (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(trans.Quantity), 0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory trans INNER JOIN MST_TranType ON trans.TranTypeID = MST_TranType.TranTypeID WHERE ProductID = locCache.ProductID AND LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND PostDate >= @FromDate AND MST_TranType.Type = 0 ) , 0)
) as BeginStock,
( IsNull( (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(trans.Quantity), 0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory trans WHERE trans.ProductID = locCache.ProductID AND trans.LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND (trans.PostDate BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) AND (trans.TranTypeID = 11) -- PO Receipt ) , 0)
+ IsNull( (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(trans.Quantity), 0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory trans WHERE trans.ProductID = locCache.ProductID AND trans.Quantity > 0 AND trans.LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND (trans.PostDate BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) AND (trans.TranTypeID = 19) -- WO Completion ) , 0)
+ IsNull( (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(trans.Quantity), 0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory trans WHERE trans.ProductID = locCache.ProductID AND trans.Quantity > 0 AND trans.LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND (trans.PostDate BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) AND (trans.TranTypeID = 21) -- WO Issue ) , 0)
+ IsNull( (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(trans.Quantity), 0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory trans WHERE trans.ProductID = locCache.ProductID AND trans.Quantity > 0 AND trans.LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND (trans.PostDate BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) AND (trans.TranTypeID = 8) -- Return Goods Receipt ) , 0) + IsNull( (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(trans.Quantity), 0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory trans --INNER JOIN WHERE trans.ProductID = locCache.ProductID AND trans.Quantity > 0 AND trans.LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND (trans.PostDate BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) AND (trans.TranTypeID = 24) -- Nhap tu location khac --AND trans.IssuePurposeID NOT IN (14) ) , 0)
+ IsNull( (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(trans.Quantity), 0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory trans WHERE trans.ProductID = locCache.ProductID AND trans.Quantity > 0 AND trans.LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND (trans.PostDate BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) AND (trans.TranTypeID = 17) -- Dieu chinh tang ) , 0)
+ IsNull( (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(trans.Quantity), 0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory trans WHERE trans.ProductID = locCache.ProductID AND trans.Quantity > 0 AND trans.LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND (trans.PostDate BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) AND (trans.TranTypeID = 25) -- Recycle Material ) , 0) + IsNull( (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(trans.Quantity), 0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory trans INNER JOIN IV_MiscellaneousIssueMaster issue ON issue.MiscellaneousIssueMasterID = trans.RefMasterID INNER JOIN MST_Bin source ON issue.SourceBinID = source.BinID AND source.BinTypeID = 3 --DS INNER JOIN MST_Bin dest ON issue.DesBinID = dest.BinID AND source.BinTypeID <> 3 --DS WHERE trans.ProductID = locCache.ProductID AND trans.Quantity > 0 AND trans.LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND (trans.PostDate BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) AND (trans.TranTypeID = 24) -- Nhap tu location khac ) , 0) ) as InQuantity,
( IsNull( (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(trans.Quantity), 0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory trans INNER JOIN MST_TranType ON trans.TranTypeID = MST_TranType.TranTypeID WHERE trans.ProductID = locCache.ProductID AND trans.LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND (trans.PostDate BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) AND MST_TranType.Type = 0 ) , 0) - IsNull( (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(trans.Quantity), 0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory trans INNER JOIN MST_TranType ON trans.TranTypeID = MST_TranType.TranTypeID WHERE trans.ProductID = locCache.ProductID AND trans.Quantity < 0 AND trans.LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND (trans.PostDate BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) AND (MST_TranType.Type = 1 OR MST_TranType.Type = 2) ) , 0) + IsNull( (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(trans.Quantity), 0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory trans INNER JOIN PRO_WorkOrderCompletion complete ON complete.WorkOrderCompletionID = trans.RefMasterID INNER JOIN MST_Bin toBin ON complete.BinID = toBin.BinID AND toBin.BinTypeID = 3 --DS WHERE trans.ProductID = locCache.ProductID AND trans.Quantity > 0 AND trans.LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND (trans.PostDate BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) AND (trans.TranTypeID = 19) -- WO Completion ) , 0)
+ IsNull( (SELECT ISNULL(SUM(trans.Quantity), 0) FROM MST_TransactionHistory trans INNER JOIN PRO_WorkOrderCompletion complete ON complete.WorkOrderCompletionID = trans.RefMasterID INNER JOIN MST_Bin toBin ON complete.BinID = toBin.BinID AND toBin.BinTypeID = 3 --DS WHERE trans.ProductID = locCache.ProductID AND trans.Quantity > 0 AND trans.LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND (trans.PostDate BETWEEN @FromDate AND @ToDate) AND (trans.TranTypeID = 11) -- PO Receipt ) , 0) ) as OutQuantity,
ISNULL( ( Case When ( SELECT SUM(cost.ActualCost) as ActualCost FROM CST_ActualCostHistory cost INNER JOIN cst_ActCostAllocationMaster cycle ON cycle.ActCostAllocationMasterID = cost.ActCostAllocationMasterID WHERE cost.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID AND (Year(cycle.FromDate) <= (case when @Month = 1 then @Year -1 else @Year end) AND Month(cycle.FromDate) <= (case when @Month = 1 then 12 else @Month-1 end) ) AND (Year(cycle.ToDate) >= (case when @Month = 1 then @Year -1 else @Year end) AND Month(cycle.ToDate) >= (case when @Month = 1 then 12 else @Month-1 end)) ) Is Not Null Then (SELECT SUM(cost.ActualCost) as ActualCost FROM CST_ActualCostHistory cost INNER JOIN cst_ActCostAllocationMaster cycle ON cycle.ActCostAllocationMasterID = cost.ActCostAllocationMasterID WHERE cost.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID AND (Year(cycle.FromDate) <= (case when @Month = 1 then @Year -1 else @Year end) AND Month(cycle.FromDate) <= (case when @Month = 1 then 12 else @Month-1 end)) AND (Year(cycle.ToDate) >= (case when @Month = 1 then @Year -1 else @Year end) AND Month(cycle.ToDate) >= (case when @Month = 1 then 12 else @Month-1 end)) ) Else (SELECT SUM(Cost) FROM CST_STDItemCost WHERE ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID) End), 0) as BeginItemCost,
ISNULL( ( Case When ( SELECT SUM(cost.ActualCost) as ActualCost FROM CST_ActualCostHistory cost INNER JOIN cst_ActCostAllocationMaster cycle ON cycle.ActCostAllocationMasterID = cost.ActCostAllocationMasterID WHERE cost.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID AND (Year(cycle.FromDate) <= @Year AND Month(cycle.FromDate) <= @Month) AND (Year(cycle.ToDate) >= @Year AND Month(cycle.ToDate) >= @Month) ) Is Not Null Then (SELECT SUM(cost.ActualCost) as ActualCost FROM CST_ActualCostHistory cost INNER JOIN cst_ActCostAllocationMaster cycle ON cycle.ActCostAllocationMasterID = cost.ActCostAllocationMasterID WHERE cost.ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID AND (Year(cycle.FromDate) <= @Year AND Month(cycle.FromDate) <= @Month) AND (Year(cycle.ToDate) >= @Year AND Month(cycle.ToDate) >= @Month) ) Else (SELECT SUM(Cost) FROM CST_STDItemCost WHERE ProductID = ITM_Product.ProductID) End), 0) as ItemCost
FROM (SELECT DISTINCT LocationID, ProductID FROM MST_TransactionHistory WHERE (Year(PostDate)= @Year) AND (Month(PostDate)= @Month) ) TransHis
INNER JOIN IV_LocationCache locCache ON TransHis.LocationID = locCache.LocationID AND TransHis.ProductID = locCache.ProductID INNER JOIN MST_Location ON MST_Location.LocationID = locCache.LocationID INNER JOIN ITM_Product ON ITM_Product.ProductID = TransHis.ProductID INNER JOIN MST_UnitOfMeasure ON ITM_Product.StockUMID = MST_UnitOfMeasure.UnitOfMeasureID LEFT JOIN ITM_Category ON ITM_Product.CategoryID = ITM_Category.CategoryID
WHERE ITM_Product.ProductID = 318 -- AND locCache.LocationID = 161
GROUP BY locCache.LocationID, locCache.ProductID, MST_Location.Code, ITM_Product.Code, ITM_Product.Description, ITM_Product.Revision, ITM_Category.Code, MST_UnitOfMeasure.Code, ITM_Product.ProductID
